{"tid":488193,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"延世大學慶典 IU宛如仙女下凡般的唯美畫面","createTime":"2017-12-03T13:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T11:02:56.000Z","uid":34643,"like":145,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b51dba52eea92157d61c995f2587e2e5cb36e692","tid":488193,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"觀眾視角<br />\n<a href=\"https://cf-e2.streamablevideo.com/video/mp4/mdkkt.mp4?token=1512306444-OIY3lImhTx8xSPlDp1HJ2T0InlccWmcPKTsTT1MVc28%3D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-e2.streamablevideo.com%2Fvideo%2Fmp4%2Fmdkkt.mp4%3Ftoken%3D1512306444-OIY3lImhTx8xSPlDp1HJ2T0InlccWmcPKTsTT1MVc28%253D&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=61e6a9a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://cf-e2.streamablevideo.com/video/mp4/mdkkt.mp4?token=1512306444-OIY3lImhTx8xSPlDp1HJ2T0InlccWmcPKTsTT1MVc28%3D</a><br />\n<br />\nIU視角<br />\n<a href=\"http://igcdn-photos-f-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xaf1/10000000_1185147714948035_4842603955844284416_n.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Figcdn-photos-f-a.akamaihd.net%2Fhphotos-ak-xaf1%2F10000000_1185147714948035_4842603955844284416_n.mp4&d=rKcJJVa6SMWng0bfshvUrmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=84d46928\" target=\"_blank\">http://igcdn-photos-f-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xaf1/10000000_1185147714948035_4842603955844284416_n.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nIU在20日出席延世大學的活動中，被網友拍下2度黑人問號回頭看的萌樣，引起不少討論。<br />\n<br />\n活動當天，IU正唱著《夜信》時，大螢幕鏡頭捕捉到了，徐徐微風吹著她的短髮，那宛如仙女下凡般的唯美畫面，讓台下觀眾紛紛不自覺發出驚呼聲。而舞台上的IU卻「不知是她太美了」，才會讓台下觀眾不停發出驚呼聲，2度好奇的轉頭看身後發生了什麼事。<br />\n<br />\n影片公開後，不少網友留言說「真的太可愛了，怎麼會有人又美又可愛的」、「IU反應好可愛」、「太美了...就像仲夏夜的女神一樣」、「這是天使吧..實在太美了」等心動的話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2538/2538112.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2538%2F2538112.jpg&h=556c2752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2538/2538113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2538%2F2538113.jpg&h=99c627cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>▲螢幕中的IU太美了，讓台下觀眾驚呼聲不斷，但IU卻不知是自己太美轉頭查看。</strong>"},{"pid":"c29574f32c12f63d520c5559b798011385139f34","tid":488193,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65590a7a1ca0195bace94c14250e559b374f5c6b","tid":488193,"uid":108236,"like":23,"dislike":16,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"e4d5eb189d32b8b739e3369b282c142b6401a8db","tid":488193,"uid":143840,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"係仙氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e241c57789484f6fd4319697293bb845e72a72c8","tid":488193,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f5827418c936d24f7244773c807ba4b402857f","tid":488193,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係仙氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca0a6fd0c34adda23fdf8df1d28c1573f3325c5","tid":488193,"uid":31725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 